msgctxt "944"
msgid "Tokita"
msgstr "Tokita"

msgctxt "120_Tokita"
msgid "Hmph. Do you really think that someone like you has what it takes to train me?"
msgstr "Hmph. Do you really think that someone like you has what it takes to train me?"

msgctxt "132_Tokita"
msgid "Hmph. I wish you could make better use of all of the amazing skills that I have."
msgstr "Hmph. I wish you could make better use of all of the amazing skills that I have."

msgctxt "144_Tokita"
msgid "Heh. You should feel lucky to have an apprentice like me."
msgstr "Heh. You should feel lucky to have an apprentice like me."

msgctxt "156_Tokita"
msgid "Heh... This dojo isn't so bad after all."
msgstr "Heh... This dojo isn't so bad after all."

msgctxt "168_Tokita"
msgid "I usually don't trust other people, but I guess I could make an exception for you. Heheh..."
msgstr "I usually don't trust other people, but I guess I could make an exception for you. Heheh..."

